---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro - Data, AI & territorial intelligence">

  <!-- ========== ENGLISH ========== -->
  <div class="lang-en">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <h1>Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">Director, JP Asesores &middot; Data, AI &amp; territorial intelligence</p>
          <p class="hero-desc">
            Consultant in innovation, data science and territorial intelligence. For 13+ years I have
            turned evidence into decisions with social organizations, communities and institutions across
            Costa Rica and Central America. My focus now: applied AI for social and collective good,
            data sovereignty, and capacity building.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
            <a href="/files/emmanuel-gutierrez-profile-en.pdf" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">Download profile</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="avatar">
          <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">13+</div><div class="stat-label">Years of experience</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">60+</div><div class="stat-label">Organizations served</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">95.1%</div><div class="stat-label">Nosara Census coverage</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">$55M+</div><div class="stat-label">Fiscal gap quantified</div></div>
      </div>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Currently</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What I'm building now</h2>
        <div class="pub-section" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Framework - Census + Fiscal Balance + Mapa de Voces de Nosara</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>History of Nosara <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Editorial project - Archival research + oral history of founding families</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Sustainable &amp; Regenerative Development for Nosara <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Applied research - Territorial reordering models grounded in the data</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Territorial Fiscal Balance - methodology replication <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Open methodology - Transferable to other districts and municipalities</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Digital Twins, Heat Maps &amp; Policy for the Future <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">R&amp;D - Real-time territorial twins + interactive policy simulation</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Agentic, Internet-AI Native Institutions <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Applied research - Governance for the era of agentic AI and an internet-native public</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.25rem;"><a href="/publicaciones" class="btn btn-outline">See full details in Publications</a></div>
      </section>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Focus</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What I work on</h2>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"/><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Territorial intelligence</h3>
            <p>Subnational fiscal and territorial balances, data systems and evidence for decisions at the district and municipal level.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Data science</h3>
            <p>Analysis, indicators and data systems that turn raw information into usable evidence for action.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon data"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Impact evaluation</h3>
            <p>Measurement of outcomes and impact for programs, projects and public interventions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon funds"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Applied AI for social good</h3>
            <p>Artificial intelligence applied to social and collective challenges, from automation to territorial analysis.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Data sovereignty</h3>
            <p>Community and territorial control over data: who collects it, who owns it, who decides with it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10L12 5 2 10l10 5 10-5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c0 1 2 3 6 3s6-2 6-3v-5"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Training &amp; education</h3>
            <p>Capacity building and education so that tools, methods and data literacy stay in the territory.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="projects">
        <p class="section-tag">Selected work</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Work with impact</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Community Census</h3><p>First district-level census in Costa Rica, with 95.1% household coverage and technical advisory from INEC. Foundation of the Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence framework.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Territorial Fiscal Balance</h3><p>First district-level fiscal study in the country. Quantified gap above USD 55M per year. Cadastral gap factor of 12.1x.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024 - 2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence</h3><p>Framework integrating fiscal analysis, census data and participatory governance (Mapa de Voces de Nosara) + SIG cartography + 30 locality reports. First field deployment: the district of Nosara.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2022 - 2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Cruz Roja Nosara - financial sustainability (MAINTERS-CRN)</h3><p>Co-design of a replicable financial sustainability model for community emergency services facing donor fatigue and growing demand.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Model</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Entrepreneurship, innovation &amp; early-stage support</h3><p>13 years of experience in entrepreneurship, innovation and early-stage venture support. Program Coordinator at Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Model</span></div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/proyectos" class="btn btn-outline">See all work</a></div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ========== ESPANOL ========== -->
  <div class="lang-es">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <h1>Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">Director, JP Asesores &middot; Datos, IA e inteligencia territorial</p>
          <p class="hero-desc">
            Consultor en innovacion, ciencia de datos e inteligencia territorial. Desde hace más de 13 anos
            convierto evidencia en decisiones junto a organizaciones sociales, comunidades e instituciones en
            Costa Rica y Centroamerica. Mi foco hoy: inteligencia artificial aplicada a lo social y colectivo,
            soberania de datos, y capacitacion.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Contacto</a>
            <a href="/files/emmanuel-gutierrez-perfil-es.pdf" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">Descargar perfil</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="avatar">
          <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">13+</div><div class="stat-label">Anos de experiencia</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">60+</div><div class="stat-label">Organizaciones atendidas</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">95.1%</div><div class="stat-label">Cobertura Censo Nosara</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">$55M+</div><div class="stat-label">Brecha fiscal cuantificada</div></div>
      </div>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Ahora</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">En lo que estoy trabajando</h2>
        <div class="pub-section" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Framework - Censo + Balance Fiscal + Mapa de Voces de Nosara</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Historia de Nosara <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Proyecto editorial - Investigacion de archivo + historia oral de las familias fundadoras</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Desarrollo sostenible y regenerativo para Nosara <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Investigacion aplicada - Modelos de reordenamiento territorial basados en datos</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Balance Fiscal Territorial - replicacion metodologica <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Metodologia abierta - Transferible a otros distritos y municipalidades</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Gemelos digitales, mapas de calor y politica publica para el futuro <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">I+D - Gemelos territoriales en tiempo real + simulacion interactiva de politica</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Instituciones nativas de Agentic e Internet-AI <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Investigacion aplicada - Gobernanza para la era de IA agentica y un publico nativo de internet</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.25rem;"><a href="/publicaciones" class="btn btn-outline">Ver detalle en Publicaciones</a></div>
      </section>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Foco</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">En qué trabajo</h2>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"/><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Inteligencia territorial</h3>
            <p>Balances fiscales y territoriales subnacionales, sistemas de datos y evidencia para decisiones a nivel distrital y municipal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Ciencia de datos</h3>
            <p>Analisis, indicadores y sistemas de datos que convierten informacion en evidencia util para la accion.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon data"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Evaluacion de impacto</h3>
            <p>Medicion de resultados e impacto para programas, proyectos e intervenciones publicas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon funds"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>IA aplicada a lo social</h3>
            <p>Inteligencia artificial aplicada a desafios sociales y colectivos, de la automatizacion al analisis territorial.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Soberania de datos</h3>
            <p>Control comunitario y territorial sobre los datos: quien los recoge, quien los posee, quien decide con ellos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10L12 5 2 10l10 5 10-5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c0 1 2 3 6 3s6-2 6-3v-5"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Capacitacion y educacion</h3>
            <p>Formacion y educacion para que las herramientas, los metodos y la alfabetizacion de datos se queden en el territorio.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="projects">
        <p class="section-tag">Proyectos destacados</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Trabajo con impacto</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Censo Comunitario de Nosara</h3><p>Primer censo a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica. Cobertura del 95.1% de hogares, con asesoria tecnica del INEC. Base del framework Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Balance Fiscal Territorial de Nosara</h3><p>Primer estudio fiscal a nivel de distrito en el pais. Brecha cuantificada superior a USD 55 millones anuales. Factor de brecha catastral de 12.1x.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024 - 2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial</h3><p>Framework que integra analisis fiscal, datos censales y gobernanza participativa (Mapa de Voces de Nosara) + cartografia SIG + 30 reportes a nivel de localidad. Primer despliegue en campo: el distrito de Nosara.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2022 - 2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Cruz Roja Nosara - sostenibilidad financiera (MAINTERS-CRN)</h3><p>Co-diseno de un modelo de sostenibilidad financiera replicable para servicios de emergencia comunitarios frente a fatiga de donantes y demanda creciente.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Modelo</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Emprendimiento, innovacion y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana</h3><p>13 anos de experiencia en emprendimiento, innovacion y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana. Coordinador de Programas en Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Modelo</span></div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/proyectos" class="btn btn-outline">Ver todos los proyectos</a></div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
